meanings: (분해·해체하다) take sth off, take sth apart, dismantle, (formal) disassemble
[뜯어서 내버리다] tear[take] ((a thing)) off and throw ((it)) away, take ((a thing)) apart[to pieces] and throw ((it)) away.
[제거하다] clear ((a thing)) away, put[take] away, remove.
